## Quick Start

### 1. Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Initialize Accounting System
```bash
python aac_engine.py
```

### 3. Start Web Dashboard
```bash
python run_aac.py --web
```
Visit: http://localhost:5000

### 4. Run Compliance Checks
```bash
python -c "from aac_compliance import ComplianceMonitor; from aac_engine import AccountingEngine; cm = ComplianceMonitor(AccountingEngine()); print(cm.check_compliance())"
```

### 5. Generate Financial Intelligence Report
```bash
python -c "from aac_intelligence import FinancialIntelligence; from aac_engine import AccountingEngine; fi = FinancialIntelligence(AccountingEngine()); print(fi.generate_comprehensive_report())"
```

